    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/d8dcb7174f6c0502ed1fec72ba483fc9.avif?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/3f8970a073d7500fda6b87efaad6b993.webp?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/467b5eb9d5fd95ab65cb6d6aeacabbef.avif?t=1716564657\" width=614 height=345 /></span><br><br>由兽王梅莉凯带领，猞猁部落与大自然有着特殊的联系。他们是骄傲的猎人，他们优秀的射箭技巧和独特的引诱技术足以保证他们子民的持续繁荣。<br><br>当优雅又极具威胁性的猞猁布兰德和凯尔琳还只是幼崽的时候，这个部落就收养了他们，把他们养大，培养他们成为了受人尊敬的首领和战场上不可忽视的力量。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/c98040f01c20c4f6f1d193cc75876a77.webp?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/20cf0b5a9cb342429d209826f5af1b2b.avif?t=1716564657\" width=614 height=220 /></span><br><br>她年轻时是凶猛的女猎手，现在是骄傲而能干的领袖，统治着北加尔的野生动物，只通过她忠诚的猞猁同伴的眼睛来观察。虽然她的高龄可能会限制她在战场上的战斗力，但她对这片土地上的动物们的至高统治力足以弥补这一点，这些野生动物将毫不犹豫地为她和她的子民而战。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/06656614853001228b43dd39a0ef3a0b.webp?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/5ab931fd29aaa04d3758dc9a5eab114e.poster.avif?t=1716564657\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/5ab931fd29aaa04d3758dc9a5eab114e.webm?t=1716564657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/5ab931fd29aaa04d3758dc9a5eab114e.mp4?t=1716564657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>梅莉凯忠实的伙伴和猞猁部落忠诚的仆从。布兰德最年轻，也更爱玩儿，但即使他看起来像一只无辜的猞猁，你也永远不要低估他可怕的猛击和战斗的威力。<br><br>作为两只猞猁中经验丰富的长者，凯尔林见识得更多，并试图保护他的弟弟和家族的人免受北加尔上的危险。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/fb1a5fe4cfc1bef4c8f6d8ead9a2206a.avif?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/cc83be33d4018811e89eca55ff7efb93.webp?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>杀死动物获得狩猎奖杯。<br></li><li>你可以召唤布兰德和凯尔林至你的训练营。<br></li><li>射箭场取代投斧手营。他们训练的追踪者是远程单位，会射出一片箭雨。<br></li><li>猎人之路取代了军事路线。花费狩猎奖杯为布兰德、凯尔林和追踪者解锁强大的技能。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/945d8989f400ec15194ad5c3c81838d2.webp?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><strong>声望200：诱饵</strong><br><br>为梅莉凯解锁神话诱饵。她可以放置诱饵，以周期性地吸引神话动物。<br><br><strong>声望500：奥斯科雷亚</strong><br><br>为梅莉凯解锁奥斯科雷亚技能。她能召唤出部落最后杀死的最强神话动物。它们以精神形态回归，在地球上进行最后的暴行。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401490/extras/41d2e69108eb952f2a0d4366a907157e.webp?t=1716564657\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br>在非敌人区域放置一个陷阱。当敌人在内的时候，可以根据需要激活，以生出长刺伤害并减慢敌人的速度。",
